data.description: Won't find anything nicer than this home in the McCall-Donnelly area for a lower price.  Bright, clean 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with open floor plan.  Bonus room is the only room not on the main level and can be used as a 4th bedroom or Media Room.  Sits on a spacious corner lot with views of the Mountains.  Maintenance friendly, with hardi-plank siding and HOA fees that cover snow plowing and lawn care.  Close to Cascade Reservoir and Tamarack Ski Resort, without the Tamarack price. Includes Hot Tub with reinforced deck and 220 power completed in 2021.  Exterior was painted in 2021 and LVP Flooring was installed in 2020.  Short term rentals are allowed.  Don't miss this one!
